name: Joe Pope
text: Very good pizza, quick and friendly service. Even had a joke in the box.

name: Spencer Zuniga
text: One of my preferred spots to grab some food. very good location, neat, and fantastic customer service. A must try!

name: Chris Wilson
text: LOVE Godfather's pizza. It is the best!!

name: UprightApes
text: Pretty decent Pizza here.. Not as good as the regular locations, I think maybe the ingredients aren't as fresh.  Also, somebody mentioned a buffet.. but this one is in a gas station.  There is no buffet.

name: Megan Quinn
text: Really good pizza. The buffet is the best.

name: Kelsey Wust
text: Great pizza. Taco pizza my favorite!
